":223216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T04:52:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e23f621980cd1bf073e432ff1a97e8718fbcfe5a","tid":1659601,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T04:55:56.000Z","msg":"城邦論"},{"pid":"2381660f0cee8d102187b370b372eb89bb84f881","tid":1659601,"uid":223216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e23f621980cd1bf073e432ff1a97e8718fbcfe5a","tid":1659601,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T04:55:56.000Z","msg":"城邦論"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T07:32:46.000Z","msg":"呢個識 仲有冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0df6a5ef433f0c2dc498c4c8dcf2a458339604b","tid":1659601,"uid":136393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15a9c74a5464d91d9931e4074a5bb466332ac853","tid":1659601,"uid":223216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T04:46:23.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n或者一啲本士論述既書<br />\n最好講埋邊個chapter特別有意思 有啟發<br />\n可以做literature review<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n主要圍繞香港<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T07:58:38.000Z","msg":"城邦論。城邦論意義在於佢切中個香港病根就係香港冇政治主體，人浮於事任人宰割赤化。而建立政治主體既手法就係靠城邦同文化構築，陳雲講既內容自己睇。內容未必個個認同，但命題我覺得係真切需要探討。<br />\n<br />\n大江東去 : 司徒華回憶錄。如果想理解同體諒泛民/社混界既政治意識既話，呢本幾重要。<br />\n<br />\n你想做咩 lit. review?"},{"pid":"c5fa0c188a7cb6a6e73d88b1cfc3ff68e7a4ac10","tid":1659601,"uid":12185,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T22:39:19.000Z","msg":"本土派論述都係果幾本<br />\n城邦：<br />\n陳雲，城邦論（三集）<br />\n<br />\n民族獨立：<br />\n學苑（梁繼平），香港民族論<br />\n徐承恩，鬱躁的城邦：香港民族源流史<br />\n<br />\n主權獨立：<br />\n梁衍華，香港獨立論<br />\n<br />\n泛自決：<br />\n方志恆，香港革新論（個人認為好流）"},{"pid":"35568ab9ed73df5ef5ff432a82f55840b3ae863e","tid":1659601,"uid":223216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T07:42:03.000Z","msg":"有冇關於制度內 議會內既書<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2baa2100f4a31b5511a0ee3a5e8a2069787c70a4","tid":1659601,"uid":223216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T08:01:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7494bd9de4cf6f893fa67584deba0e6611f49316","tid":1659601,"uid":166350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T09:50:32.000Z","msg":"Contentious politics- Charles Tilly"},{"pid":"be5fc830a2446d9114bce9ea64138fb8753b3641","tid":1659601,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T14:08:02.000Z","msg":"周保松"},{"pid":"3086d2885086185d306b5c81a18fbfad781515ec","tid":1659601,"uid":258097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T15:00:58.000Z","msg":"酒神的抗爭"},{"pid":"ff7255c966215603897a653fffa224507bf05d87","tid":1659601,"uid":80510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T15:12:14.000Z","msg":"失治之城：掙扎求存的香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.books.com.tw/products/0010820010\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.books.com.tw%2Fproducts%2F0010820010&d=o%2BN67aGUGKsADGfJqajrgEzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=39517b2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.books.com.tw/products/0010820010</a><br />\n講香港施政，多數據同文獻，唔知岩唔岩?"}]}